Package: bar
Title: Simulation And Least Squares Estimation of the Buffered Autoregressive Model
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Daan", "de Jong", email = "d.dejong@uu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The buffered autoregressive (BAR) model describes a time series that follows 
	one of two possible AR processes according to a hysteretic switching mechanism.
	With 'bar', you can simulate data from this model and estimate parameter values
	based on data. 
